Class DatabaseAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • Resort.Utility.DatabaseAgent

  • public class DatabaseAgent
extends java.lang.Object
    Database CRUD(Create, Retrieve, Update, Delete) class. Handles the methods for making connections to the database and manipulating the data in it.
